OL,3,CMan flown to Southampton with "serious
OL,4,Cinjuries" following motorbike crash
OL,6,FA man has been flown to Southampton
OL,7,FHospital with "serious injuries" after
OL,8,Fcrashing his motorbike in the early
OL,9,Fhours of this morning (7 March).
OL,11,FThe 31-year-old was injured when his
OL,12,Fblack Yamaha XJR1300 motorbike
OL,13,Fcollided with a wall on La Vier Mont
OL,14,Fin Grouville at around 5am.
OL,16,FPolice arrived at the scene shortly
OL,17,Fafter and were assisted by colleagues
OL,18,Ffrom both the Fire and Ambulance
OL,19,FServices.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
