CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772979077
OL,3,CMan flown to Southampton with "serious
OL,4,Cinjuries" following motorbike crash
OL,6,FThe man was treated on scene by
OL,7,Fparamedics before being transported to
OL,8,FJersey's hospital, where the decision
OL,9,Fwas made to transport him to the UK
OL,10,Fdue to the seriousness of his injuries.
OL,12,FA major part of Longueville Road and
OL,13,FLa Rue a Don were closed for several
OL,14,Fhours whilst officers conducted their
OL,15,Finvestigation, but they have since
OL,16,Freopened.
OL,18,FHowever, Le Vier Mont remains closed.
